      FraustoLLC is the site you're on right now. It is a static site, made using <a href="http://haml.info/" target="_blank">haml</a>, <a href="http://coffeescript.org/" target="_blank">coffeescript</a>, and <a href="http://sass-lang.com/" target="_blank">sass</a>. You can view the source code at <a href="https://github.com/frausto/frausto.github.com" target="_blank">github</a>.

    .bgov.description.hidden
      Bgov.com is a Rails app run by Bloomberg dedicated to organizing government data including but not limited to news, grants, contracts, congressional staff, federal regulation, etc...

    .director.description.hidden
      Resque Director is ruby gem for the <a href="https://github.com/defunkt/resque" target="_blank">Resque</a> queueing system. It automatically adds/removes workers based on the length of the queue, or how long it takes for a job to go through. 
      
